STARLING

CUSTOMER REFERRAL PROGRAM TEMPLATE

The Starling Template is an excellent option for your customer referral program. This referral program template empowers your advocates with all the tools they need to successfully share your products, monitor referral activity, and get paid. It is ideal for your e-commerce referral program, allows multiple payment options (PayPal, gift cards, and vouchers), and it's available in 20 languages.

This customer referral program template is built with Bootstrap 4 Framework, HTML5, CSS3, and JQuery. It is easily customizable, fully responsive, and supports all current browsers and devices.

TRY IT NOW
LIVE PREVIEW

No sign up required

This customer referral program template has no traditional registration and login forms. Registration is provided via a seamless access form where your advocates must enter their email addresses. You can also skip this step by using our one-click access link tool or add your custom fields to this access form to collect additional information from your advocates.

The advocate statistics section delivers deep insight into their referral program account, allowing the advocate to review their performance and focus on the advocacy tools that work. The advocate can quickly check the total referrals and rewards, the list of referrals, bonuses, and their status.

ADVOCATE INSIGHTS

ADVOCATE PAYMENT METHODS

Multiple advocate payment methods are available on this customer referral program template, and you can activate various advocate payment methods to allow your advocates to choose their preferred payment method. Vouchers, store credit, and store gift cards are the best advocates payment method options available when building a customer referral program.
